messages.message: Hi team/ @lydia - in the 24.07 platform upgrade, are there going to be any LLM updates ? RSA are wanting to know so they can understand/ prepare how to approach and plan resource allocation for the upcoming AI Hub migration cc @hannah
yes, there are. Let me follow-up with Jean on release notes for LLM changes

Thank Lydia - do we know how we can help customers prepare for this change? I know there were converations around customers testing new LLMs to make any prompt changes. RSA will want to know how we can avoid what happened last time cc @Aimé
@Bhuvnesh Gupta can you check this in the upcoming release standup please and share an update with the team?
